{"tid":1815582,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020DSE自修] 英文卷一同卷二既Mock (11/1/2020)","createTime":"2020-01-07T15:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T07:08:10.000Z","uid":125535,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6cc7567029fe84cf7e349553dd5b277c569772","tid":1815582,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"又係我, 阻到大家既話唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次做左一次Paper 3既Mock, 今次係<span style=\"color: red;\">Paper 1&amp; 2</span>, 考完之後邀請左日校英文科老師即場解卷。今次老師會<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">即場改埋</span>Paper 2, 俾完分後會即時派返俾大家。<br />\n<br />\n仲有名額剩, 誠邀自修英文既巴絲打參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期: 11/1/2020 (星期六)<br />\n地點: 美孚既社區中心<br />\n對象: 24歲或以下既自修生 (冇讀緊書嗰種)<br />\n名額: 20人<br />\n費用: 80蚊 (包埋lunch, 收費主要想避免甩底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 一蚊都冇賺; 今次老師會改文, 所以比上次貴左少少)<br />\n<br />\n流程<br />\n10:00-12:00 Paper 2 模擬試 (120分鐘)<br />\n12:00-13:30 午膳<br />\n13:30-15:00 Paper 1 模擬試 (90分鐘)<br />\n15:00-15:30 小休 <br />\n15:30-17:30 Paper 1 + Paper 2 模擬試解卷 + Q&amp;A環節<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲打可以係Google Form留低聯絡方法, 我再PM大家詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/fev4qKnbkAy1u6sK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Ffev4qKnbkAy1u6sK6&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9cb53f98\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/fev4qKnbkAy1u6sK6</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">完左可以問埋老師讀書意見<br />\n利申: 社福機構舉辦既, 已作補貼, 冇賺大家錢架</span></span>"},{"pid":"0589043fc00136408a90d469bf0accf671c16199","tid":1815582,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c76f1dd715c5d98050991da4f7ae0e1fd5fc22","tid":1815582,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:48: